            <title>[LU-11780] interop: replay-single test 132a fails with &apos;&apos;Component #1 instantiation was not replayed&apos;&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11780</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;replay-single test_132a was added to the Lustre test suites for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11158&quot; title=&quot;PFL component instantiation is not replayed properly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11158&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-11158&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; with patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32847/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/32847/&lt;/a&gt; . This test will fail for all Lustre servers with version less than 2.12.0. Thus, we need to add a version check for replay-single test 132a.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
